summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing negotiation for and acquisition of easements required for the construction of the southwest Kenyon Street Sanitary Sewer Project across certain property in Lots 2 to 10, Block 14, State Addition No. 4, and application to the Highway Commission, Department of Highways for a sewer franchise across State Route 509 in the vicinity of Southwest Kenyon Street, and authorizing payment therefor.
